reviews.text:
Damm, my favourite custard so far!!&#xD;
&#xD;
So creamy and thick, I went for the extra INW custard and FA Meringue additions and I’m absolutely loving it.&#xD;
&#xD;
I especially love the Ice cream element which gives it extra decadence and the cereal makes it more interesting than a standard custard adding another dimension.&#xD;
&#xD;
Simple but rich, thick, luxurious and  bloody delicious, exactly what I was looking for for an ADV&#xD;
&#xD;
It was delicious straight off the shake with the ice cream being fairly prominent and after a one week steep the cereal aspect showed its face and everything balanced out superbly. All these flavours work so well together and I haven’t stopped vaping it all week which is uncommon for me as I get bored easily &#xD;
&#xD;
Great recipe
